{"title":"在故乡的原野上（二首）","authors":["左一兵"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":1,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在故乡的原野上（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左一兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风呵，风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风是故乡的骄子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在没有疆界的原野"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱着属于母亲的自由的歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有标题，没有句号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她不需要休止符号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约束奔放的感情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的旋律是明快的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴随着脱粒机的节奏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和打谷场上的笑声揉合，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄浑而深沉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗犷而快活，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升华了庄重的思想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把浪漫的情思撩拨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风，原野游动的歌手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一支进行曲送到遥远的村落。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故乡的梦，不再荒凉、苦涩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月，在屋檐下……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农家的喜悦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏在屋檐下挂着的果实上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串，一串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金黄的，桔红的，翠绿的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在清风中飘荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一首香喷喷的诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤起故乡最初的遐想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难怪小伢儿吵吵嚷嚷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她要读诗，要品味，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她要沿着诗行走向远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去丰富幼稚的想象。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母亲笑了，动情地笑了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的笑是成熟的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泥土，给了她分量！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}